'Sergio is one of the best strikers in the world, for sure – he is in the top five,' Zabaleta told the Manchester Evening News as part of City in the Community's new Walking Football programme.’

'As a City player I would love to see one of our players get nominated for the Ballon d'Or, and we have a very strong squad with top players.

